and throw it in the trash bin.

06:06.889 --> 06:08.720
Let me get this right...

06:08.889 --> 06:10.242
...shithead!

06:11.849 --> 06:13.248
You kill me.

06:13.409 --> 06:16.845
-You think I was a terrific Juliet--
-You were!

06:17.009 --> 06:22.083
