on the East Side.

09:00.889 --> 09:04.643
But when you wake up,
you'll find she's not very serious.

09:04.809 --> 09:06.686
Neither am l.

09:06.849 --> 09:09.124
Harry, listen to me.

09:09.289 --> 09:13.328
For the first time in our lives,
we're free.

09:13.489 --> 09:16.640
Yeah, free to walk in the cold.
To be ridiculed.

09:16.809 --> 09:18.322
I don't mean that.

09:18.489 --> 09:23.005
I mean we're free to get out
of this city. It's driving me buggy.

09:23.369 --> 09:25.405
What are you trying to pull?

09:25.569 --> 09:28.083
I gave you a $10 bill.
Think I'm crazy?

09:28.249 --> 09:30.399
