09:30.569 --> 09:34.244
-You gave me a buck, not 10.
-Bullshit! I gave you a 10!

09:34.409 --> 09:39.403
-Why are you trying to steal from me?
-Get lost, Chico.

09:40.969 --> 09:44.962
See what this city does to people?
They need room to breathe.

09:45.129 --> 09:47.120
They need love, affection!

09:47.289 --> 09:52.522
