in a civilized manner?

11:04.489 --> 11:05.922
It's okay with me.

11:08.049 --> 11:10.404
By the way, sir, what is your name?

11:12.529 --> 11:13.882
Alex.

11:14.409 --> 11:16.684
Alex. And you, sir?

11:16.849 --> 11:19.602
-My name is Chico.
-Chico.

11:20.169 --> 11:25.004
Alex, may I present Chico.
Chico, this is Alex.

11:25.169 --> 11:26.887
How do you do?

11:30.209 --> 11:32.677
Wallet. Wallet.

11:32.849 --> 11:35.363
Okay. Okay.

11:38.169 --> 11:40.729
-Here. Here.
-Hey, thanks, sir.

11:40.889 --> 11:44.325
