-Yes. Have it all. Okay?

11:44.489 --> 11:45.888
Thanks a lot.

11:46.049 --> 11:49.598
I'll leave you. You seem
to have a friendship starting.

11:49.769 --> 11:52.124
-Have a nice evening.
-Thank you.

11:52.289 --> 11:55.008
-So long, fellas.
-So long.

11:55.209 --> 11:56.767
Take care.

11:59.049 --> 12:01.199
No, no, don't. That--

12:08.969 --> 12:11.563
